title: Oziexplorer All Mediteranean Sea (harbors)
description:
Maps of all the Gulf mediteranean
 
Archive includes Data ; Maps; Name search

To install the maps simply decompress everything where OziExplorer reads the MAP files
(Eg: D:OziExplorerMaps)
.WPT files can be copied where OziExplorer reads the data
(Eg: D:OziExplorerData)
and
files with extension NAMES and TYPES should be copied where OziExplorer reads the names
(Eg: D:OziExplorerName Search)

 .................Mostly for sailors
